ive Cloud subscription model.", "IBM is an American multinational technology corporation headquartered in Armonk, New York, founded in 1911. It pioneered mainframe computing, created the Watson AI platform, and holds a vast portfolio of technology patents."], "scores": [0.8092482212293394, 0.6561005783942208, 0.6396998671689237, 0.6366353988276562, 0.6361855895708123], "model_name": "bge-base", "document_ids": ["Apple", "Microsoft", "Intel", "Adobe", "IBM"]}}